{"tid":899256,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屯門空氣指數達10+　東涌元朗也瀕爆表 (17:04)","createTime":"2018-11-12T09:40:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-12T10:59:23.000Z","uid":75969,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f529b95f5cbad4b5f5edda440310bbe53bb5975d","tid":899256,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T09:40:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181112/s00001/4820045cd22add45bf54ac57ab321af1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181112%2Fs00001%2F4820045cd22add45bf54ac57ab321af1.jpg&h=21c77c4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本港現時空氣污染嚴重。據環保署空氣質素健康指數顯示，截至下午4時，港九新界各個路邊及一般監測站的指數由7至10+不等。<br />\n<br />\n其中，香港西面3個一般監測站為重災區。屯門空氣指數為10+，健康風險為嚴重；元朗和東涌空氣指數為10，健康風險甚高。<br />\n<br />\n環保署表示，本港受背景污染較高的氣團影響（尤其是臭氧、PM10和PM2.5），而微弱的風勢亦不利污染物擴散。日間的陽光有利光化煙霧現象，令臭氧及微細懸浮粒子在珠江三角洲區域內迅速形成。特別在巿區部分地區及路邊，較高的臭氧水平亦會加速二氧化氮的形成。<br />\n<br />\n根據香港天文台表示，東北季候風現正影響廣東沿岸，本周中後期本港東風增強及有一兩陣雨。環保署預料在風勢增強之前，本港的空氣污染仍會維持在較高的水平。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181112/s00001/1542013274726\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181112%2Fs00001%2F1542013274726&d=F77gZwdEA7vBqSzj0okTB2xr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=d5b3140a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181112%2Fs00001%2F1542013274726&h=3402d054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181112/s00001/1542013274726</a>"},{"pid":"80ed416fe10004da06c635a52533d8ab6e64b4c1","tid":899256,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T09:44:36.000Z","msg":"好臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5690731b6cc678bf76f0cc011140e7ba8a607c70","tid":899256,"uid":6968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T09